    "body": "Here is how to replicate\r\n\r\n```\r\nnpx hardhat node --fork https://api.avax.network/ext/bc/C/rpc --fork-block-number 17154874\r\n\r\ncurl -s --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"debug_traceTransaction\",\"params\":[\"0x9f8b8623b643e0d930163528ccd56bc0fe087f1ee27510d1ca0a0b6a4217aac6\"],\"id\":\"1\"}' -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -X POST http://localhost:8545\r\n```\r\nactual gas usage is `136,573` hardhat reports gas usage `109,259`\r\nhttps://snowtrace.io/tx/0x9f8b8623b643e0d930163528ccd56bc0fe087f1ee27510d1ca0a0b6a4217aac6\r\n",
